What is the maximum file upload size?
text: No more than 2GB. All files in your account must fit your allotted storage space.

title: How do I reset my password?
text: On your Android phone or tablet, open your device's Settings app Google. Manage your Google Account.

title: Can I cancel my subscription?
text: Cancel the subscriptions by emailing the service providers.

title: Do you provide additional support?
text: We fully support the principle of providing additional support to those with the most critical care needs.
